column2: select * from OPENQUERY([CBIO],&&&' &&&) as case_ids  from cancer_study cs    inner join sample_list sl      on sl.CANCER_STUDY_ID=cs.CANCER_STUDY_ID  join sample_list_list sll     on sl.list_id=sll.list_id  join sample s    on s.internal_id=sll.sample_id where cs.cancer_study_identifier=&&&hnsc_jhu&&& group by sl.stable_id,sl.cancer_study_id order by #,#')
